{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Description</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready for some epic, bouncy action in <i>Battle Balls</i> \u2014 the ultimate 4-player online and local multiplayer 3D platform fighter and party game! Choose your favorite ball and prepare to throw down against friends or AI in wild battles and wacky mini-games. Each ball has unique attacks, and the ability to use turbo, shield, jump, and dash. Some balls are giant and tough, others are tiny and speedy, but every single one is special and ready to get freaky!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025900/extras/TowerSiegeOptimized.gif?t=1737154600\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Local</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Battle </strong>-<strong> </strong>Choose your arena and jump into the action! Compete in thrilling 3D battles with multiple lives and a whole bunch of crazy platforms. Grab items to boost your stats or use them to sabotage your opponents. It\u2019s a free-for-all \u2014 only the strongest (and most strategic) balls will survive!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mini-Games </strong>-<strong> </strong>The fun doesn\u2019t stop at the battles, it's time to play with your balls! Challenge your friends in over 20 silly mini-games to find out who has the best balls of them all. Ready for chaos, laughs, and some seriously crazy competition?</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tournament </strong>-<strong> </strong>Think you\u2019ve got what it takes to win it all? Select a number of rounds and jump into a tournament of mini-games! Each round is a new challenge, and the better you perform, the more points you\u2019ll rack up. At the end, the player with the most points gets to claim the crown \u2014 and bragging rights!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025900/extras/LaserJumpOptimized.gif?t=1737154600\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Online</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take your balls global! Join or create lobbies to compete in battles and mini-games with players from all over the world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Discord</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join the <i>Battle Balls</i> Discord server to find other <i>Battle Ballers</i> and stay up to date on all the latest news and updates! Let\u2019s get the ball rolling!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Get the game while it's in Early Access for 2 exclusive ball skins!</i></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Baby Battle Baller","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1025900/230be16dd05d435bbe6f7bc4635e8a9df747b421.jpg"},{"name":"Novice Battle Baller","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1025900/544e398bd8d1b17bd29bb90424736c13d3dbdd4f.jpg"},{"name":"Adept Battle Baller","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1025900/88d35c0d43f9a76d0de1eb492d4c7d223e9aa7d7.jpg"},{"name":"Expert Battle Baller","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1025900/d8694c2d7bea4bcdba99a5d1817080489f2b7aa7.jpg"},{"name":"Master Battle Baller","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1025900/e603b23421c044e4ecac515c3a9a9e82206414c5.jpg"}],"total":5},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025900/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737154600","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025900/page.bg.jpg?t=1737154600","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025900/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737154600",